U.K. Defense Equipment Scrapping to Cost $19 Billion, Times Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-02-14T01:38:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/u-k-defense-equipment-scrapping-to-cost-19-billion-times-says.html
The scrapping of equipment by the
U.K. military will cost 12 billion pounds ($19 billion), the
London-based Times reported, without saying where it got the
information. An additional 2.3 billion pounds of defense
materiel has been designated as “lost,”  Danny Alexander , chief
secretary to the Treasury will tell Parliament today, the
newspaper said.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
